message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper focuses on deep learning for medical image segmentation, which is a common topic in the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) communities. Additionally, the paper specifically addresses the issue of imbalance in both the input and output of the learning model, which is a common problem in medical image analysis. This makes it likely that the paper could also be classified under the medical imaging (cs.MED) and neural networks (cs.NEURON) sub-categories.
